&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;The 911 caller, 62-year-old Garry Dean Mode, reported he had just been involved in an altercation with an acquaintance he had invited to his home. Mode reported he had used multiple weapons during the dispute. When officers arrived, they found the victim, a 45-year-old Bend resident, with serious injuries in the driveway. The victim was transported to St. Charles Bend. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

