&lt;p&gt;For more information,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://www.oregon.gov/oha/hpa/hp/pages/affordability-committee.aspx" style="text-size-adjust: 100%; color: rgb(6, 66, 118);"&gt;please visit the committee&rsquo;s website&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

