&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:14pt"&gt;More information about &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;E. coli&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:14pt"&gt;: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a class="Hyperlink SCXW8845741 BCX8" href="https://www.cdc.gov/ecoli/about/index.html" rel="noreferrer noopener" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:14pt"&gt;https://www.cdc.gov/ecoli/about/index.html&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:14pt"&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:14pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
