&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW87977382 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;: 61000 block of Camelot Place, Bend &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW87977382 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Missing: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;Stephen Alan Baer, 74-year-old Bend resident&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW87977382 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;Bend Police are asking for the public&rsquo;s assistance in locating a missing Bend man. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW87977382 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;Stephen Alan Baer, 74, was last seen by family members when he left his home on Camelot Place in southeast Bend at approximately 5 p.m. on Sunday, Oct. 26. He was driving a white Ford E350 van with Oregon license plate 085 JKW. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW87977382 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;Baer did not bring his medications with him. Without those medications, he can suffer from memory issues and other medical problems. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW87977382 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;Baer is described as a white male adult, 5 feet 9 inches and 180 pounds with gray hair. He was last seen wearing a navy blue windbreaker, a blue-and-white striped T-shirt and jeans, with black sneakers. He wears glasses. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW87977382 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;Because he has been without his medication for an extended period, he is now considered endangered. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;If you see Baer or his vehicle, please call nonemergency dispatch at 541-693-6911 or 911. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

