     &lt;li&gt;Trauma Subcommittee:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://www.zoomgov.com/j/1614516532?pwd=plCM3iwYwtvDgKkaB2JcNnhPj3Joxb.1" style="text-size-adjust: 100%; color: rgb(6, 66, 118);"&gt;Zoom&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
